1. Kupio sam *polovinu* kilograma jabuka. (I bought half a kilogram of apples.)
2. *Polovinu* svoje plate trošim na kiriju. (I spend half of my salary on rent.)
3. Ovaj kolač sam iseckao na *polovine*. (I cut this cake into halves.)
4. *Polovina* stanovništva Srbije živi u gradovima. (Half of the population of Serbia lives in cities.)
5. Još jednu *polovinu* moramo da završimo pre večere. (We have to finish one more half before dinner.)
6. *Polovinom* leta planiram da otputujem u Grčku. (I plan to travel to Greece in the middle of summer.)
7. *Polovina* problema je već rešena. (Half of the problem is already solved.)
8. Nemoj da jedeš *polovinu* kolača, ostavi i meni. (Don't eat half of the cake, leave some for me.)
9. Moramo da podelimo troškove na *polovine*. (We have to split the costs in half.)
10. Juče sam pročitao *polovinu* knjige. (Yesterday, I read half of the book.)